# Minimal, reproducible Python dependencies for DINO-X.
#
# Notes:
# - Prefer generating a fully-pinned requirements.txt from this file via pip-tools
#   (or by installing and re-freezing inside .venv).
# - Keep this list small; add packages as they are introduced into src/scripts.

